The '''Sarawak Fire Horse B.C.''' are a [[Malaysia]]n [[basketball]] team that competed in the [[Malaysia National Basketball League]] and based in [[Miri, Malaysia|Miri]], [[Sarawak]], [[Malaysia]].

==History==
{{Empty section|date=May 2014}}

==Home Arenas==
The Sarawak Fire Horse B.C. home venue list is as follows:-

* [[Miri Indoor Stadium]] - 2011–present

